# SceneSetupSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
One-shot scene builder. Returns early until both SandboxConfigSingletonComponent and
ResourceMapSingletonComponent are present. On the first ready frame it creates the
scene camera, the static demo sprite, the arrow-key-controlled animated character (a SpriteComponent +
an 8x8 SpriteAnimationComponent + a CharacterTagComponent, starting idle), a 3D model entity (a
ModelComponent referencing the configured model resource by UUID, for the forthcoming 3D scene), and
the world-space labels (a title, an instructions label, and a tagged input-readout label), emitting a
SceneTransformRequestOneFrameComponent to seed each one's world transform (position-only for the
camera). It also emits a LoadLayoutEvent to load the UI layout and creates SceneReadySingletonComponent
as its run-once guard.

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SandboxConfigSingletonComponent | read | Font/texture/model/layout ids for the scene; guard (returns early if absent) |
| ResourceMapSingletonComponent | read | Guard only: ensures the layout load will resolve |
| SceneReadySingletonComponent | read | Run-once guard |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| OrthographicCameraComponent | add (deferred) | Scene camera; the app CameraControlSystem drives it via the engine CameraSystem |
| SpriteComponent | add (deferred) | Engine component; the static demo sprite and the animated character's sprite |
| SpriteAnimationComponent | add (deferred) | Engine component; the character's 8x8 sprite-sheet animation state (starts idle), driven by the engine SpriteAnimationSystem |
| ModelComponent | add (deferred) | Engine component; references the configured 3D model resource by UUID, placed by its world transform for the forthcoming 3D render pass |
| CharacterTagComponent | add (deferred) | Marks the character for CharacterControlSystem |
| LabelComponent | add (deferred) | Title, instructions and the input-readout label |
| SceneTransformRequestOneFrameComponent | add (oneframe) | Seeds the world transform for the camera, sprite and labels |
| InputReadoutTagComponent | add (deferred) | Marks the readout label for InputReadoutSystem |
| LoadLayoutEvent | add (deferred) | Emitted once to load the UI layout |
| SceneReadySingletonComponent | add (deferred) | Run-once guard |
